name: DD_DIA_CMS_START
description: This table contains data elements submitted for CMS ESRD patient registration forms (CMS-2728).

columns.name: REGISTRY_DATA_ID
columns.description: The unique identifier for the registry data record.

columns.name: FORM_IDENTIFIER
columns.description: The CMS 2728 form identifier.

columns.name: DLYS_REG_FORM_TYPE_C_NAME
columns.description: The CMS 2728 form type, such as initial registration or reentitlement.

columns.name: ADMISSION_DEPARTMENT_ID
columns.description: The patient's dialysis admission facility that is submitting this CMS 2728 form.

columns.name: PAT_FIRST_NAME
columns.description: The patient's first name.

columns.name: PAT_MIDDLE_INITIAL
columns.description: The patient's middle initial.

columns.name: PAT_LAST_NAME
columns.description: The patient's last name.

columns.name: DLYS_NAME_SUFFIX_C_NAME
columns.description: The patient's name suffix.

columns.name: DLYS_PAT_SEX_C_NAME
columns.description: The patient's sex assigned at birth.

columns.name: PAT_BIRTH_DATE
columns.description: The patient's date of birth.

columns.name: PAT_HICNUM
columns.description: The patient's Medicare health insurance claim number.

columns.name: PAT_MBI_NUM
columns.description: The patient's Medicare Beneficiary Identifier number.

columns.name: PAT_SSN
columns.description: The patient's Social Security number.

columns.name: MAIL_ADDRESS_STREET_1
columns.description: The first line of the street address of the patient's mailing address.

columns.name: MAIL_ADDRESS_STREET_2
columns.description: The second line of the street address of the patient's mailing address.

columns.name: MAIL_ADDRESS_CITY
columns.description: The city of the patient's mailing address.

columns.name: MAIL_ADDRESS_TAX_STATE_C_NAME
columns.description: The state of the patient's mailing address.

columns.name: MAIL_ADDRESS_COUNTY_2_C_NAME
columns.description: The county of the patient's mailing address.

columns.name: MAIL_ADDRESS_ZIP_EXT
columns.description: The ZIP code extension of the patient's mailing address.

columns.name: PHONE_AREA_CODE
columns.description: The area code of the patient's phone number.

columns.name: PHONE_NUMBER
columns.description: The patient's phone number, minus the area code.

columns.name: DLYS_PAT_CNTRY_OF_ORG_C_NAME
columns.description: The patient's country of origin.
entries: Congo, The Democratic Republic of the
Korea, Democratic People's Republic of (North Korea)
Macedonia, The Former Yugoslav Republic of
South Georgia and South Sandwich Islands

columns.name: DLYS_PAT_ETHNICITY_C_NAME
columns.description: The patient's ethnicity.

columns.name: PAT_TRIBE_CODE
columns.description: The patient's tribe code.

columns.name: DLYS_ETH_SELF_REP_C_NAME
columns.description: Whether the patient's race and ethnicity were self-reported.

columns.name: ESRD_MEDICARE_APPLY_YN
columns.description: Whether the patient is applying for end stage renal disease Medicare coverage.

columns.name: PRIOR_DLYS_EMPY_STATUS_C_NAME
columns.description: The patient's employment status six months prior to renal failure.

columns.name: CURRENT_DLYS_EMPY_STATUS_C_NAME
columns.description: The patient's current employment status.

columns.name: PAT_HEIGHT
columns.description: The patient's height.

columns.name: DLYS_HEIGHT_UNIT_C_NAME
columns.description: The unit used for the patient's height.

columns.name: PAT_DRY_WEIGHT
columns.description: The patient's dry weight.

columns.name: DLYS_WEIGHT_UNIT_C_NAME
columns.description: The unit used for the patient's weight.

columns.name: DIA_CMS_GFR_METHOD_C_NAME
columns.description: The method used to calculate the patient's glomerular filtration rate (GFR).

columns.name: PRIM_CAUSE_RENAL_FAIL_DX_ID
columns.description: The ICD-10 CM code of the patient's primary cause of renal failure.

columns.name: EPO_RECEIVED_DIA_CMS_YNU_C_NAME
columns.description: Whether the patient received exogenous erythropoietin (EPO) or equivalent prior to end stage renal disease therapy.

columns.name: EPO_DIA_CMS_DATE_RANGE_C_NAME
columns.description: The time range in which exogenous erythropoietin (EPO) or equivalent was administered to the patient prior to end stage renal disease therapy.

columns.name: NEPH_CARE_RECV_DIA_CMS_YNU_C_NAME
columns.description: Whether the patient was under nephrologist care before starting end stage renal disease therapy.

columns.name: NEPH_CARE_DIA_CMS_DATE_RANGE_C_NAME
columns.description: The time range in which the patient was under nephrologist care prior to end stage renal disease therapy.

columns.name: DIET_CARE_RECV_DIA_CMS_YNU_C_NAME
columns.description: Whether the patient was under kidney dietician care prior to end stage renal disease therapy.

columns.name: DIET_CARE_DIA_CMS_DATE_RANGE_C_NAME
columns.description: The time range in which the patient was under kidney dietician care prior to end stage renal disease therapy.

columns.name: DIA_CMS_FIRST_ACCESS_C_NAME
columns.description: The type of access used for the first outpatient dialysis treatment prior to end stage renal disease therapy.

columns.name: MATURE_AVF_PRESENT_YN
columns.description: Whether the patient had a maturing arteriovenous fistula (AVF) present prior to end stage renal disease therapy.

columns.name: MATURE_AVG_PRESENT_YN
columns.description: Whether the patient had a maturing arteriovenous graft (AVG) present prior to end stage renal disease therapy.

columns.name: DLYS_TRT_LOCATION_C_NAME
columns.description: The primary setting in which the patient receives dialysis treatment, such as the patient's home, a dialysis treatment center, skilled nursing facility, or long-term care facility.

columns.name: DLYS_TRT_TYPE_C_NAME
columns.description: The type of dialysis treatment the patient receives, e.g. hemodialysis or peritoneal dialysis.

columns.name: DIALYSIS_SESSIONS_PER_WEEK
columns.description: The number of hemodialysis sessions per week prescribed for the patient.

columns.name: DIALYSIS_SESSION_LENGTH_HOURS
columns.description: The duration, in hours, of hemodialysis sessions prescribed for the patient.

columns.name: CHRONIC_DIALYSIS_START_DATE
columns.description: The date the patient began a regular course of dialysis treatments.

columns.name: FACILITY_TREATMENT_START_DATE
columns.description: The date the patient began receiving dialysis treatments at the current facility.

columns.name: TXP_OPTIONS_PROVIDED_YN
columns.description: Whether the patient has been informed of their options for receiving a kidney transplant.

columns.name: ATTENDING_PROV_ID
columns.description: The patient's attending provider for dialysis treatments.

columns.name: ATTENDING_PROV_REMARKS
columns.description: Miscellaneous remarks entered by the patient's attending provider.

columns.name: LAB_ALBUMIN_VALUE
columns.description: The patient's serum albumin lab value.

columns.name: LAB_ALBUMIN_DATE
columns.description: The patient's serum albumin lab collection date.

columns.name: LAB_ALBUMIN_LOWER_LIMIT
columns.description: The patient's serum albumin lab lower limit value.

columns.name: LAB_ALBUMIN_METHOD_C_NAME
columns.description: The patient's serum albumin lab method.

columns.name: LAB_CREATININE_VALUE
columns.description: The patient's serum creatinine lab value.

columns.name: LAB_CREATININE_DATE
columns.description: The patient's serum creatinine lab collection date.

columns.name: LAB_HEMOGLOBIN_VALUE
columns.description: The patient's hemoglobin lab value.

columns.name: LAB_HEMOGLOBIN_DATE
columns.description: The patient's hemoglobin lab collection date.

columns.name: LAB_HBA1C_VALUE
columns.description: The patient's glycated hemoglobin (HbA1c) lab value that was collected within 45 days prior to the first dialysis treatment or kidney transplant (whichever is more recent).

columns.name: LAB_HBA1C_DATE
columns.description: The patient's glycated hemoglobin (HbA1C) lab date that was collected within 45 days prior to the first dialysis treatment or kidney transplant (whichever is more recent).

columns.name: LAB_LIPID_TC_VALUE
columns.description: The patient's lipid profile total cholesterol lab value that was collected within one year prior to the first dialysis treatment or kidney transplant (whichever is more recent).

columns.name: LAB_LIPID_TC_DATE
columns.description: The patient's lipid profile total cholesterol lab date that was collected within one year prior to the first dialysis treatment or kidney transplant (whichever is more recent).

columns.name: LAB_LIPID_LDL_VALUE
columns.description: The patient's lipid profile LDL cholesterol lab value that was collected within one year prior to the first dialysis treatment or kidney transplant (whichever is more recent).

columns.name: LAB_LIPID_LDL_DATE
columns.description: The patient's lipid profile LDL cholesterol lab date that was collected within one year prior to the first dialysis treatment or kidney transplant (whichever is more recent).

columns.name: LAB_LIPID_HDL_VALUE
columns.description: The patient's lipid profile HDL cholesterol lab value that was collected within one year prior to the first dialysis treatment or kidney transplant (whichever is more recent).

columns.name: LAB_LIPID_HDL_DATE
columns.description: The patient's lipid profile HDL cholesterol lab date that was collected within one year prior to the first dialysis treatment or kidney transplant (whichever is more recent).

columns.name: LAB_LIPID_TRIGLYCERIDES_VALUE
columns.description: The patient's lipid profile triglyceride lab value that was collected within one year prior to the first dialysis treatment or kidney transplant (whichever is more recent).

columns.name: LAB_LIPID_TRIGLYCERIDES_DATE
columns.description: The patient's lipid profile triglyceride lab date that was collected within one year prior to the first dialysis treatment or kidney transplant (whichever is more recent).

columns.name: TRAINING_DEPARTMENT_ID
columns.description: The patient's dialysis training facility.

columns.name: TRAINING_START_DATE
columns.description: The start date for the patient's dialysis training.

columns.name: TRAINING_END_DATE
columns.description: The end date for the patient's dialysis training.

columns.name: TRAINING_DLYS_TRT_TYPE_C_NAME
columns.description: The type of training given to a patient in preparation for dialysis treatment.

columns.name: DLYS_SELFCARE_STATUS_C_NAME
columns.description: Whether the patient is expected to perform self-care at home or in-center after dialysis training.

columns.name: SELF_DIALYZE_YN
columns.description: Whether the patient will self-dialyze after completing dialysis training.

columns.name: TRAINING_PROV_ID
columns.description: The patient's provider for dialysis training.

columns.name: MAIL_ADDRESS_ZIP
columns.description: The ZIP code of the patient's mailing address.
